Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: pysandra
Version: 0.2.1
Summary: Python driver for Cassandra focusing on asyncio users.
Home-page: https://github.com/toppk/pysandra
Author: Kenneth Topp
Author-email: toppk@bllue.org
License: MIT or Apache License, Version 2.0
Description: ## Goals
        
        * cassandra client driver for asyncio based applications
        * allow doing anything the wire protocol allows
        
        ## Implementation
        
        Currently targeting python 3.6 and above
        
        Aims to be:
        
        * correct
        * fast
        * efficient
        * developer friendly
        
        ## Todos
        
        * Tests
        * TLS
        * AUTH
        * typing
        
        ## Developing
        
        $ cd pysandra
        $ python3 -m venv venv
        $ source venv/bin/activate
        $ pip install -r test-requirements.txt
        $ pip install -e .
        
        
